&lt;p&gt;Since August 2019, we’ve been making it easier for customers to find the right vehicle, and for automotive retailers to sell them.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;More recently, we’ve been on a journey…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In June 2025 we were acquired by Volkswagen Financial Services UK (VWFS UK) and our mission is simple: build the right tech solutions for Volkswagen Group UK and its retailers, so they can deliver the best possible experiences to their customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re a mix of problem-solvers, innovators, and team players who care about doing great work and making a difference. We thrive on collaboration, innovation, and a shared commitment to excellence. We deliver impactful solutions at pace that put the customer at the centre.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re looking for a meaningful challenge, and want to help shape the future of automotive experiences, then read on…&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join the team and play a pivotal role in building highly scalable and maintainable backend services. You&#39;ll have the opportunity to leverage and suggest the latest tools and techniques, collaborating closely with Product, Design, and Sales teams. We encourage sharing technical solutions and product ideas through code and design reviews, pair programming, and presentations, all while continuously improving our Agile processes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our culture empowers our talented developers to develop using whichever tools we need to get the job done. To face the many challenges, including brilliant customer experience, data processing,&amp;nbsp; microservice architecture and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands on building highly scalable and maintainable backend services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use appropriate tools for development and being proactive in suggesting new tools, frameworks or techniques&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate across functional teams including Product, Design and Sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share technical solutions and product ideas through code and design reviews, pair programming, and presentations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highlight areas we can improve on as a team practising Agile processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Tech Stack:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We use the tools we need to get the job done. We primarily use the following tools and frameworks (some have been added in the past year, and more are planned):&lt;/p&gt;
