&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical skills to build scalable backend services, primarily in Python (in any framework)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical skills: a love for problem solving, and improving our working processes.&amp;nbsp; We are always learning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A good understanding of databases, OO design, data structures and SOLID principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong desire to work collaboratively with both your peers and business teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to communicate technical concepts to other members of the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
